{"tid":494313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=?? 地盤開工　28歲工人遭噸重工字鐵擊斃","createTime":"2017-12-09T13:26:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-11T08:46:03.000Z","uid":19454,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"f0c8ce8649972f054f1720a46a507b5e60337b9e","tid":494313,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T13:26:08.000Z","msg":"石硤尾發生奪命工業意外，早上11時許，白雲街白田邨重建地盤，有工字鐵吊運期間懷疑墮下，擊中一名姓麥(28歲)工人頭部重創，送院不治。據悉，死者未婚，家住將軍澳，從事建造業逾一年，任職鐵器工，與任職燒焊工的父親及一名胞弟同在該地盤工作，死者當時正與胞弟及其他工友搬運工字鐵，但懷疑沒有清場。家屬事後趕至醫院，驚聞噩耗傷心不已。警方及勞工處已派員到地盤調查意外原因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171209/bkn-20171209140508572-1209_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171209%2Fbkn-20171209140508572-1209_00822_001.html&d=I9q57khBnM14iE4uKaveFp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=feab1389\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171209/bkn-20171209140508572-1209_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f20ff16d93aa51b1079547216e223da476ef617e","tid":494313,"uid":41818,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T13:38:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39dd37e73e3d654b91a291db18946a4f00352bbf","tid":494313,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T13:40:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3f5fe7335d22479c32257208674f8cf90c3f09c","tid":494313,"uid":24660,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T14:34:46.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"95936a058295ab492e34dba3c96e35ce9b09fa62","tid":494313,"uid":20241,"like":5,"dislike":34,"score":-29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T15:25:28.000Z","msg":"用家問題<br />\n地盤總括來講都係好安全既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c41bf75ebc6ac7c5033852c8bb388e2d6b94c2a","tid":494313,"uid":389,"like":26,"dislike":5,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2