ote><blockquote>地盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲水後生仔入行</blockquote><br />\nok<br />\n後生仔唔入行<br />\n咁等輸入外勞<br />\n俾d南亞同大陸黎做</blockquote><br />\n好事 建築成本又平左</blockquote><br />\n好事?<br />\n到時D老師傅死晒<br />\n又無人識做<br />\n佢地揀撚住你春袋加人工啦</blockquote><br />\n星加坡比人鍊春袋未</blockquote><br />\n如果真係輸入外勞，到時香港仲多蝻同蝗，點解唔好好由香港人舊帶新做落去？<br />\n香港啲師父人工係高，但手勢一定好過南亞同中國工人"},{"pid":"dc1b5f2910447620b78427499b0f10b972de093c","tid":494313,"uid":127716,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T02:09:10.000Z","msg":"如果冇後生做建築工人 <br />\n其他高學歷既全部做管理層<br />\n到時得返大陸人做真係唔好怨"},{"pid":"a4596e246cca85126bc028c1fd4b6bb73fe96425","tid":494313,"uid":69681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T02:10:38.000Z","msg":"呢啲整定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nRip"},{"pid":"35189946f07875b7061e9fc614afcc9b62dce60f","tid":494313,"uid":71877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T02:14:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>南亞人死左咪掟落垃圾車</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc774664a3183c53446984dd58be5c63a651225c","tid":494313,"uid":49004,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T02:16:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三父子做 加埋7-8皮一個月<br />\n爽yy</blockquote><br />\n諗起奇幻潮<br />\n屋企人許願想要錢 點知換來個仔地盤工作死咗有賠償金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後結局話我乜都唔想要 身邊一切全部消失晒<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaf21f8f9f296c134a1204048c8cedff83d9094b","tid":494313,"uid":23846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T02:17:57.000Z","msg":"係咁話無後生做點點點<br />\n而家個個月一單地盤死人 叫d後生點入行？<br />\n點同屋企人講去做地盤？老豆老母個個月睇新聞都驚一次？"},{"pid":"d070444c8413bfef38ab61efb7c2aab9edf2354f","tid":494313,"uid":67338,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T02:18:59.000Z","msg":"忽視安全.亂放D野.<br />\n<br />\n老果班又會話 O靚仔乜野駛唔駛咁多帶咁多安全野阻手阻腳呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結果再加埋可能存在既神秘力量咪搞到依類結果羅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bfaeac72127e2ee324d5f36257a11caf6e78e8a","tid":494313,"uid":67338,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T02:23:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咁話無後生做點點點<br />\n而家個個月一單地盤死人 叫d後生點入行？<br />\n點同屋企人講去做地盤？老豆老母個個月睇新聞都驚一次？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做乜野工都有危險性<br />\n<br />\n不過工程地盤都算係其中兩項最常有老手叫新手忽視安全既工作.你係新人唔想羅命搏,但係老手會叫你唔駛咁既.做左咁多年都無事.帶左仲唔安全仲阻住哂做唔到野.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n若果你依然堅持要帶.班老手會唔happy.埋唔到堆架"},{"pid":"607a3da32810c13f7836ea72295be2d92ab7dff6","tid":494313,"uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T02:29:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/492583/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/492583/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n早幾日先有新聞叫人做燒焊 琴日死左個好似就係做燒焊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"632c0f331f1bda7621e6d102867f1b39ef9ad140","tid":494313,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T02:32:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/492583/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/492583/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n早幾日先有新聞叫人做燒焊 琴日死左個好似就係做燒焊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又係老貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"effc3b9a912ce92441af6f768ef50e34e2254f29","tid":494313,"uid":55990,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T02:55:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8ceddb0313ad2bc1f93f297cdc5de21a89b6a024","tid":494313,"uid":35644,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T03:00:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港狗廢青死多啲</span></span></blockquote><br />\n屌你老母 祝你全家生癌 長病百歲<br />\n人地出黎賺血汗錢遇到意外仲要俾你咁講<br />\n<br />\nbtw r.i.p<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab322ed4e227459b4aa7d78c1263e28c657e7095","tid":494313,"uid":124107,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T03:17:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4a16a6ffa1eaa19abaa05240fb7d094f5b26fd0c","tid":494313,"uid":16956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T03:23:35.000Z","msg":"依d真係唔好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b07a8ecea01b982a15794033982b6e937605269e","tid":494313,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T03:27:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>地盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲水後生仔入行</blockquote><br />\nok<br />\n後生仔唔入行<br />\n咁等輸入外勞<br />\n俾d南亞同大陸黎做</blockquote><br />\n好事 建築成本又平左</blockquote><br />\n好事?<br />\n到時D老師傅死晒<br />\n又無人識做<br />\n佢地揀撚住你春袋加人工啦</blockquote><br />\n星加坡比人鍊春袋未</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講到尾都係人地識選高端人口，香港政府專選低端人口"},{"pid":"e4c33df85386200703d7c197647d81e925c72dc2","tid":494313,"uid":59511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T03:30:16.000Z","msg":"我以前成日屌d工友做野唔安全，不過班友hea鳩我就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nE家我求其唔洗揹鑊就由鳩佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08fd1b8ec28243b75f232641fec6a15707c81f6f","tid":494313,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T03:31:15.000Z","msg":"有時有扣安全帶都冇用，扣住個位都唔穩陣，連人帶平台一齊跌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講到尾，只係常識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8274ddab8157c925b6222e24a0ee351183bdf515","tid":494313,"uid":156527,"like":1,"